GMT alignment:
Stepan Manukhov (04/05/2022)

1) Removed MuDst, copied event.root to a separate folder
2) In the folder with macros:
myterm@rcas $ root -l -b
.L StGmtQAPlotter.C+
.L GmtChain.C
GmtChain("/gpfs01/star/scratch/manukhov/files",".root","OutputFileName.root")
3) I copied the TDraw.C code from the star/u/gnigmat/macr/gmt/TDraw.C directory, then in the macros
folder:
root -l -b OutputFileName.root TDraw.C+
The result is two files:
Results.Barrel_-1_OutputFileName
Results.Barrel_-1_OutputFileName.h

